Package: snappershadowcopy2
Version: 0.2-1
Priority: optional
Architecture: i386, amd64
Maintainer: debejerry <debejerry@gmail.com>
Homepage: http://github.com/debejerry/snapperShadowCopy2
Depends: debhelper (>= 9.0.0 ), snapper (>= 0.2.4), snamba (>= 3.6.6), python3-gi (>= 3.2.2), python-dbus (>= 1.1.1), build-essential
Description: Wrapper service around snapper (http://snapper.io) and samba with shares 
 that have the vfs module shadowCopy2 enabled, so that snapper created snapshots 
 appear on the previous version tab in Windows Explorer.
